        options: ["The patient has systemic lupus erythematosus","The positive ANA is likely a false positive in this low pre-test probability population; ANA is found in 5-15% of the general population without autoimmune disease","The patient has rheumatoid arthritis","The patient requires immediate immunosuppressive therapy"],
